3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new method that involves mapping the far-view region to its crowd density map, which involves the use of machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with analyzing crowd events in images, which is a multimedia application. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also possible as the paper deals with analyzing and processing images, which is a graphics application.
